{
    "message": "Item was successfully deleted"
}

-------------------Product-----------------

1. Get products
Method: GET
URL: /api/products

Request: -

Response:
[
    {
        "id": 1,
        "productName": ...,
        "description": ...,
        "category": {
            "id": 1,
            "categoryName": ...
        },
        "manufacturer": {
            "id": 1,
            "manufacturerName": ...,
            "country": ...
        },
        "price": ...,
        "quantity" ...
    },
    {
    }
]


2. Get product by id
Method: GET
URL: /api/products/{productId}

Request: -

Response:
{
    "id": 1,
    "productName": ...,
    "description": ...,
    "category": {
         "id": 1,
         "categoryName": ...
    },
    "manufacturer": {
        "id": 1,
        "manufacturerName": ...,
        "country": ...
    },
    "price": ...,
    "quantity" ...
}


3. Add product
Method: POST
URL: /api/products

Request: -
{
    "id": 1,
    "productName": ...,
    "description": ...,
    "category": 1,
    "manufacturer": 1,
    "price": ...,
    "quantity": ...
}

Response:
{
    "id": 1,
    "productName": ...,
    "description": ...,
    "category": {
         "id": 1,
         "categoryName": ...
    },
    "manufacturer": {
        "id": 1,
        "manufacturerName": ...,
        "country": ...
    },
    "price": ...,
    "quantity"
}


4. Delete product
Method: DELETE
URL: /api/products/{productId}

Request: -

Response:
{
    "message": "Product was successfully deleted"
}


-------------------Cart Item-----------------

1. Get Cart Items
Method: GET
URL: /api/cartItems

Request: -

Response:
[
    {
        "product": {
            "id": 2,
            "productName": ...,
            "description": ...
            "category": {
                "id": 1,
                "categoryName": ...
            },
            "manufacturer": {
                "id": 1,
                "manufacturerName": ...,
                "country": ...
            },
            "price": ...,
            "quantity" ...
        },
        "quantity": ...,
        cart: {
            "id": 1,
            "user": {
                "id": 1,
                "username": ...,
                "createDate": ...,
                "lastVisitData" ...
            }
        }
    },
    {
    }
]


2. Get Cart Items by id
Method: GET
